     At the bottom of the Skills and Abilities panel is the "Known Abilities" section (framed). You should see a number to the right of the ability name. This is what it will cost you to develop the ability one level higher
     To learn more about an ability, place the cursor over it and read the text which appears in the Descriptions panel.

     To develop an ability, click on the appropriate icon in the "Known Abilities" section.
     To confirm or cancel, click on the appropriate buttons in the "Your Experience" section.

     Note: each time you develop an ability, you increase the cost of developing other abilities.
